  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要画一个流程图，展示用户如何通过Wizelit平台调用各种工具。核心思路是把工具调用分成两类：简单的同步调用和复杂的异步任务。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "User",
        "Wizelit",
        "Tool",
        "JobMgr"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白。Wizelit平台内部包含Chainlit界面、主Agent和外部Agent，对吧？用户先通过Chat Interface连进来？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "User",
        "Wizelit",
        "Chat Interface"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，用户通过Chat Interface接入Wizelit。然后Wizelit不直接调工具，中间要过一个Universal Wrapper层，用来做标准化封装。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Wizelit",
        "Wrapper",
        "Universal Wrapper"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我把Ingestion Layer画成一个子图，里面放Standardized Agent Wrapper。Wizelit通过MCP Protocol连到这个Wrapper。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Wizelit",
        "Wrapper",
        "MCP Protocol"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "Wrapper出去要分叉。Type A是同步调用，走Fast路径，直接调Simple Tool、SQL或者RAG这类简单工具，结果立即返回。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Wrapper",
        "Tool",
        "Type A",
        "Sync Call Fast"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "同步这条线我理清楚了：Wrapper→Tool，标注Type A: Sync Call Fast，然后Tool把Result Immediate返回给Wrapper，再回传给Wizelit。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Wrapper",
        "Tool",
        "Wizelit",
        "Result Immediate"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "Type B是异步路径，处理Complex Script或者Workflow。这里要引入Job Manager，Wrapper把任务扔给JobMgr，但不用等结果。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Wrapper",
        "JobMgr",
        "Type B",
        "Async Job Slow",
        "Script"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "异步流程有点复杂，我梳理一下步骤。Step 1是JobMgr启动Script；Step 2 JobMgr要先把Job ID返回给Wizelit，让用户知道任务创建了？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "JobMgr",
        "Script",
        "Wizelit",
        "Job ID"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 9,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "没错，Step 2是Return Job ID。然后Step 3 Wizelit可以轮询状态或者流式看日志，这两步都是虚线，表示非阻塞的交互。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Wizelit",
        "JobMgr",
        "Poll Status",
        "Stream Logs"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 10,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "虚线关系我标好了。最后Step 4是Script执行完通知JobMgr，Job Complete。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Script",
        "JobMgr",
        "Job Complete"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 11,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "repair",
      "utterance": "等等，Step 4之后JobMgr需要把最终结果回传给Wizelit吗？现在图上好像断掉了，用户怎么知道任务完成了？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "JobMgr",
        "Wizelit",
        "Result"
      ],
      "is_repair": true
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 12,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "我的理解是Step 3的轮询或者流式日志已经包含了最终结果的推送，所以不需要额外画一条线。还是说你要显式画一条JobMgr到Wizelit的结果返回？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "JobMgr",
        "Wizelit",
        "Step 3",
        "Step 4"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 13,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "你说得对，Step 3的Poll Status/Stream Logs已经覆盖了结果获取，保持现状更简洁。不过Wrapper到Wizelit的那条Result线要保留，那是同步路径的返回。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Wrapper",
        "Wizelit",
        "Result"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 14,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "检查一遍：同步路径Wizelit→Wrapper→Tool→Wrapper→Wizelit，闭环；异步路径Wizelit→Wrapper→JobMgr→Script，然后Script→JobMgr，JobMgr虚线连Wizelit做状态交互。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Wizelit",
        "Wrapper",
        "Tool",
        "JobMgr",
        "Script"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 15,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "异步那里再确认一下，JobMgr到Wizelit有两条虚线：一条是Step 2返回Job ID，一条是Step 3轮询状态，方向都是双向的感觉，但标注要清晰。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "JobMgr",
        "Wizelit",
        "Step 2",
        "Step 3"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
